<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_label/><action_name/><action_query>false</action_query><action_run_at>server</action_run_at><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><application/><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_g_nci_esr_ticket</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Calculate Priority For Q-Branch</name><onclick/><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><read_access_action>false</read_access_action><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	// Add your code here
	var impact = current.getValue('impact');
	var urgency = current.getValue('urgency');
	gs.debug("Impact & Urgency" + urgency);
	
	var priority = impact * urgency;
	
	if (priority == 1) {
		current.setValue('priority',1);
	} else if (priority == 2) {
		current.setValue('priority',2);
	} else if (priority == 4 || priority == 3) {
		current.setValue('priority',3);
	} else if (priority == 6) {
		current.setValue('priority',4);
	} else {
		current.setValue('priority',5);
	}
	

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>saxenap2@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-05-03 01:50:09</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>930459651b2050102701b913cc4bcb66</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Calculate Priority For Q-Branch</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="esr" source="x_g_nci_esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_930459651b2050102701b913cc4bcb66</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>scottrym@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-24 20:23:50</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_fix_b0f460df1baad8106daea681f54bcba0
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_fix"><sys_script_fix action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><before>false</before><description/><flush_cache>false</flush_cache><name>ESR Implementation - Journal Fields</name><record_for_rollback>false</record_for_rollback><run_once>true</run_once><script><![CDATA[var oldESR = new GlideRecord("u_engineering_project_support");
oldESR.query();
while (oldESR.next()) {
var oldID = oldESR.getUniqueValue();
var tnum = oldESR.getValue('number');
var newesr = new GlideRecord("x_g_nci_esr_ticket");
newesr.get("legacy_number", tnum);
if (newesr.isValidRecord()) { 
var tid = newesr.getUniqueValue();
var oldrec = new GlideRecord("sys_journal_field");
oldrec.orderBy("sys_created_on");
oldrec.addQuery("element_id", oldID);
oldrec.query();
while (oldrec.next()) {
    var newrec = new GlideRecord("sys_journal_field");
    newrec.initialize();
	newrec.autoSysFields(false);
	newrec.setWorkflow(false);
    newrec.setValue("sys_created_on", oldrec.getValue("sys_created_on"));
    newrec.setValue("sys_created_by", oldrec.getValue("sys_created_by"));
    newrec.setValue("element", oldrec.getValue("element"));
    newrec.setValue("element_id", tid);
    newrec.setValue("name", newesr.getTableName());
    newrec.setValue("value", oldrec.getValue("value"));
    newrec.insert();
}
}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_fix</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-08-15 19:03:45</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b0f460df1baad8106daea681f54bcba0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ESR Implementation - Journal Fields</sys_name><sys_package display_value="esr" source="x_g_nci_esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_fix_b0f460df1baad8106daea681f54bcba0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-15 19:03:45</sys_updated_on><unloadable>false</unloadable></sys_script_fix></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_map"><sys_transform_map action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><copy_empty_fields>false</copy_empty_fields><create_new_record_on_empty_coalesce_fields>false</create_new_record_on_empty_coalesce_fields><enforce_mandatory_fields>No</enforce_mandatory_fields><name>ESR Q-Branch Data Migration</name><order>100</order><run_business_rules>false</run_business_rules><run_script>true</run_script><script><![CDATA[(function transformRow(source, target, map, log, isUpdate) {

	if (source.u_phase == "Phase 0: Q-Branch") {
		target.phase = 0;
		target.autoSysFields(false);
		if (source.u_state == "Backlog") {
			target.state = 2;
		} else if (source.u_state == "Work in Progress") {
			target.state = 7;
		} else if (source.u_state == "On Hold") {
			target.state = 3;
		} else if (source.u_state == "Closed Complete") {
			target.state = 9;
		} else if (source.u_state == "Closed Incomplete") {
			target.state = 10;
		} else if (source.u_phase == "Not Yet Started") {
			target.phase = 0;
			target.state = 2;
		}
	} else {
		ignore = true;
	}

})(source, target, map, log, action==="update");]]></script><source_table>x_g_nci_esr_esr_data_migration</source_table><sys_class_name>sys_transform_map</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>scottrym@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-05-11 21:04:29</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>7649ead41b30dc102701b913cc4bcb01</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ESR Q-Branch Data Migration</sys_name><sys_package display_value="esr" source="x_g_nci_esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_map_7649ead41b30dc102701b913cc4bcb01</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-15 16:55:20</sys_updated_on><target_table>x_g_nci_esr_ticket</target_table></sys_transform_map></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_fix"><sys_script_fix action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><before>false</before><description/><flush_cache>false</flush_cache><name>ESR Q Branch - Copy Attachments</name><record_for_rollback>false</record_for_rollback><run_once>true</run_once><script><![CDATA[var legacyTix = new GlideRecord('u_engineering_project_support');
legacyTix.addQuery('u_phase=0');
legacyTix.query();

while (legacyTix.next()) {
	var donorTable = 'u_engineering_project_support';
	var donorID = legacyTix.getValue('sys_id');
	var newTix = new GlideRecord('x_g_nci_esr_ticket');
	newTix.get('legacy_number', legacyTix.getValue('number'));
	if (newTix.isValidRecord()) {
		var recipientTable = 'x_g_nci_esr_ticket';
		var recipientID = newTix.getValue('sys_id');
		GlideSysAttachment.copy(donorTable, donorID, recipientTable, recipientID);
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_fix</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-08-13 12:39:46</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>7c5d34261b2218106daea681f54bcb01</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ESR Q Branch - Copy Attachments</sys_name><sys_package display_value="esr" source="x_g_nci_esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_fix_7c5d34261b2218106daea681f54bcb01</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-13 12:39:46</sys_updated_on><unloadable>false</unloadable></sys_script_fix></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><map display_value="ESR Q-Branch Data Migration">7649ead41b30dc102701b913cc4bcb01</map><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[(function runTransformScript(source, map, log, target) {

	//var snum = source.getValue("number");
	var snum = source.u_number;
	var oldesr = new GlideRecord("u_engineering_project_support");
	//oldesr = get("number",snum);
	oldesr.addQuery("number",snum);
	oldesr.query();
	oldesr.next();
	var sid = oldesr.getUniqueValue();
	gs.info("Test1 snum " + snum);
	gs.info("Test1 sid " + sid);
	
	var tnum = target.number;
	var newesr = new GlideRecord("x_g_nci_esr_ticket");
	newesr.addQuery("number",tnum);
	newesr.query();
	newesr.next();
	var tid = newesr.getUniqueValue();
	gs.info("Test2 " + tid);
	
	var oldrec = new GlideRecord("sys_journal_field");
	oldrec.orderBy("sys_created_on");
	oldrec.addQuery("element_id",sid);
	oldrec.query();
	while (oldrec.next()) {
		gs.info("Test3 beginning");
		target.setValue("comments", "Test Comments");
		target.setValue("work_notes", "Test Work Notes");
		//var newrec = new GlideRecord("sys_journal_field");
		//newrec.initialize();
		//newrec.newRecord();
		//newrec.setValue("sys_created_on", oldrec.getValue("sys_created_on"));
		//newrec.setValue("sys_created_by", oldrec.getValue("sys_created_by"));

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_fix_e27db0261b2218106daea681f54bcbc5
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_fix"><sys_script_fix action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><before>false</before><description/><flush_cache>false</flush_cache><name>ESR Implementation - Copy Attachments</name><record_for_rollback>false</record_for_rollback><run_once>true</run_once><script><![CDATA[var legacyTix = new GlideRecord('u_engineering_project_support');
legacyTix.addQuery('u_phaseIN1,2,3,4');
legacyTix.query();

while (legacyTix.next()) {
	var donorTable = 'u_engineering_project_support';
	var donorID = legacyTix.getValue('sys_id');
	var newTix = new GlideRecord('x_g_nci_esr_project');
	newTix.get('legacy_number', legacyTix.getValue('number'));
	if (newTix.isValidRecord()) {
		var recipientTable = 'x_g_nci_esr_project';
		var recipientID = newTix.getValue('sys_id');
		GlideSysAttachment.copy(donorTable, donorID, recipientTable, recipientID);
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_fix</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-08-13 12:40:10</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e27db0261b2218106daea681f54bcbc5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ESR Implementation - Copy Attachments</sys_name><sys_package display_value="esr" source="x_g_nci_esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="esr">f9c5731b1bb7c8502701b913cc4bcb5d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_fix_e27db0261b2218106daea681f54bcbc5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>lawlorap@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-13 12:40:10</sys_updated_on><unloadable>false</unloadable></sys_script_fix></record_update>
